
'''Of Good Report''' ni filime y’urukundo yo muri [[Afurika]] y'epfo yakinwe 2013, iyobowe na Jahmil XT Qubeka<ref>https://www.cnn.com/2013/08/21/world/africa/of-good-report-movie-ban/index.html</ref> . Filime yari ifite Mothusi Magano na Petronella Tshuma mu nshingano zabo<ref>http://www.mnestudies.com/report-writing/qualities-and-characteristics-good-reports</ref>. Mu bihembo bya 10 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards, yari bifite ibihembo byinshi , kandi yegukana igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy Academy cya Filime Nziza<ref>http://compassfilms.is/productions/of-good-report/</ref> <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/of-good-report/</ref>.  Iyi filime yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto 2013<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/of_good_report<nowiki/>Of Good Report – Cast & Crew on MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › of-good-report › cast</ref>. 

Muri Nyakanga 2013, mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 34 rya Durban<ref>https://variety.com/2013/film/global/of-good-report-review-1200798187/</ref>,<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/oct/14/of-good-report-london-film-festival-review</ref> filime yatoranijwe mbere yo gufungura iri serukiramuco yatangaje ko yabujijwe na Fondasiyo y’igihugu ya Filime na Video kubera ko irimo "porunogarafiya y’abana", iki cyemezo cyaje gukurwaho nyuma y’ubujurire n'abatunganya firime<ref>https://www.nfvf.co.za/home/index.php?ipkArticleID=8</ref>. 

